PageTitle: display mpls te cspf tedb network-lsa
FuncDef: The display mpls te cspf tedb network-lsa command displays information about CSPF-based TEDBs that meet specified conditions.
CLIs: display mpls te cspf tedb network-lsa
display mpls te cspf tedb network-lsa igp-type isis
display mpls te cspf tedb network-lsa igp-type ospf
Examples: <HUAWEI> display mpls te cspf tedb network-lsa
ID   DR-Router-ID    DR-Address      Area       DR-ISIS-System-ID     Neighbors
ExtraInfo:
Usage Scenario
The display mpls te cspf tedb network-lsa command displays information about CSPF-based TEDBs that meet specified conditions on the control board.
